.jumbotron
  %h1.display-3 Orders from DJI
  %p.lead
    The following has the status of 
    %strong Mavic Pro
    shipments. This is used to
    be able to know where/when your order might ship. It helps you to get an idea of how the queues are
    shipping. Right now we need more realtime data to do further analysis on, so please consider contributing
    your order information.
    
%p.alert.alert-info
  To contribute your own data, install the DJI command-line tools at
  = link_to 'http://github.com/kevinelliott/dji'
  and be sure to specify the
  %strong --publish
  option.


%table.table.table-sm.table-striped.table-middle
  %thead.thead-inverse
    %tr
      %th Order ID
      %th DJI Forum Username
      %th Order Time
      %th Payment Status
      %th City
      %th Region
      %th Country
      %th Shipping Status
      %th Shipping Company
      %th.text-xs-right Last Changed
      %th.text-xs-right Last Reported

  %tbody
    - @orders.each do |order|
      %tr
        %td.text-xs-left
          = order.masked_order_id
        %td.text-xs-left= order.dji_username
        %td= order.order_time
        %td= order.payment_status
        %td= order.shipping_city
        %td= order.shipping_region_code
        %td= order.shipping_country
        %td{ class: order.shipping_status_class }
          = order.shipping_status
        %td= order.shipping_company
        %td.text-xs-right
          = time_ago_in_words order.last_changed_at
          ago
        %td.text-xs-right
          = time_ago_in_words order.updated_at
          ago